      {
        "kind": "youtube#video",
        "etag": "DZyN9DtFeeCBej6X01Vi9xn6-fI",
        "id": "_SHh08uFK6A",
        "snippet": {
          "publishedAt": "2023-02-07T01:01:08Z",
          "channelId": "UCBp9SM5icJ40sD9ovecI4Pw",
          "title": "#SecretsSelfmadeBillionaires 1750 #ArthurDantchik  #Gambler to #Trader #Billionaire #SIG #JeffYass",
          "description": "Arthur Dantchik is a very secretive trader and billionaire.  He was probably born in 1958,  but we don't know where.  We know he is Jewish from his charitable donation to Israel.   He went to Bayside High School in Queens, New York.  In 1979,  he earned a degree in Biology from State University of New York at Binghamton.  Most importantly,  his roommate there was Jeff Yass, a future $30 Billion trader and his future business partner.  After graduation,  Arthur Dantchik and Jeff Yass moved to Las Vegas and became professional trader.  In 1987,  he , Jeff Yass and 5 others co-founded Susquehanna International Group (SIG).  They named the company Susquehanna after the river that flows past Binghamton into Pennsylvania.  SIG specializes in two things: first is ETF or Exchange Traded Funds and second is option trading.   Arthur Dantchik is best known as the China Hand, because he was the pioneer that invested in ByteDance, the parent company of Tik Tok.  After Tik Tok became a global phenomenon, it was said SIG made $30 Billion out of this investment.  In February 2023,  he has a net worth of $7.5 Billion and he is 65 year old.  The secret of his success is he is the trainer of trader and he used poker games to train his traders,  true to the origin of his firm.",
